* background "forest_bg.png"

You step into the forest.
The trees close in around you.
* flush

* temp depth, 0

* while depth < 2
    You venture deeper...
    * set depth, depth + 1
    * flush

* set score, score + 5

* choice
    # Continue deeper
        * goto_scene forest_deep
    # Go back to town
        * goto_scene town
